Darkfate::

Darkfate lead them to the mess hall. When he arrived he saw Chamaleon 
giving a Drillbit a glass of energin, it was the first that Chamaleon 
had given.

"Chameleon" said the dragon.

"Yes sir" and looking to drillbit "I'll be right back, sir"

Chamaleon and Darkfate left the room.
